{"tid":786502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚係旺角連續比兩個人問同一條問題","createTime":"2018-08-20T03:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T12:53:08.000Z","uid":42637,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a9d144b44191097fb878985658f5041086a3db61","tid":786502,"uid":42637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:25:04.000Z","msg":"琴晚等人個陣見仲有時間 就邊行邊等人 <br />\n行到銀城個頭無啦啦有個廿歲頭既男人問我「小姐知唔知邊到可以買蛋糕」<br />\n我比佢嚇親之後話唔知 下一秒佢就消失咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十分鐘之後又有個廿歲頭既大陸人又問我同一條問題 我又話唔知 <br />\n佢 小姐你幫我諗下啦我個朋友生日啊<br />\n我 地鐵站咪有囉<br />\n佢 個啲我睇過啦 唔係好啱心水<br />\n我 咁我唔知啦<br />\n佢 佢就黎生日你覺得我送咩比佢好啊<br />\n我 我真係唔知啊<br />\n講完就跑走咗 真係好恐怖連續兩個人都問同一條問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲以為係啲咩最新騙案 但上google搵又冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4d9801fc376dbb09a6cbd4b24b294fa02e3e66","tid":786502,"uid":200641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T04:01:10.000Z","msg":"啱先我又係咁俾人問<br />\n之後上網搵睇下係咪新騙案<br />\n之後就入咗黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d389de8a9c424bc4bc937949c0090f5404a4a7fe","tid":786502,"uid":105511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T04:08:51.000Z","msg":"係咪迷魂黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1ab9be013bbc604cbc364e9ba96f5552c2cfdb","tid":786502,"uid":89348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T04:14:42.000Z","msg":"我都試過呀屌 係沙田等人無啦啦走黎問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見佢著成套suit咁 我真心以為佢想買蛋糕 你答邊間佢都話唔啱 問問下佢會問埋你攞電話話做個fd 我死都唔肯比 佢就話佢唔係壞人 識個朋友姐 之後我見我朋友到 9秒9跑走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後一段時間 我又見到同一個人係到圍班學生妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e01303e355e1e293724eefd79ca7076f9355e52","tid":786502,"uid":22633,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T04:22:40.000Z","msg":"似係傳銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地好鐘意成team 人搵唔到新客就度啲on9任務出黎一齊做<br />\ne.g.今日一齊用一個理由去識20 個新朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622833272081344baf121166d3dc16a8cd3d4134","tid":786502,"uid":42637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T04:56:06.000Z","msg":"如果我真係帶佢哋去蛋糕鋪佢哋係咪真係會買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421d0540b3beb423024a4435cb08b8dc13ec5b5d","tid":786502,"uid":6675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"622833272081344baf121166d3dc16a8cd3d4134","tid":786502,"uid":42637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T04:56:06.000Z","msg":"如果我真係帶佢哋去蛋糕鋪佢哋係咪真係會買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T05:01:06.000Z","msg":"唔係好啱心水~"},{"pid":"4fd970f2a34ada74538156a71ff3d83223131c40","tid":786502,"uid":29756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T12:53:08.000Z","msg":"嗯"}]}